name: Teamkeep
overview:
Teamkeep is a free online sports team management website with an intuitive, responsive interface that can be used on any device. With Teamkeep captains and coaches can store their schedule and roster information into a customizable team home page, track player availability, and message their entire team quickly and easily, even from their mobile phone.

Interface features

  • Scheduling - all your events in one place
  • Roster - your player’s contact info
  • Home page - free, customizable home page for your team
  • Availability - track who’s coming to your events
  • Messaging - message everyone in one step
  • Privacy - control what the public sees
  • Mobile - responsive interface works on any device
